# Git & Deploy

## Branch strategy
- `main` — production (auto-deploys to Cloudflare Pages)
- `dev` — staging / integration
- `feat/xxx` — feature branches, PR into `dev`
- `fix/xxx` — hotfix branches

## Commit message format (Conventional Commits)
```
feat(hero): add parallax clip-path reveal on scroll
fix(3d): dispose geometry on canvas unmount
perf(images): convert PNG to WebP for gallery section
refactor(gsap): extract tilt animation into gsapUtils
style(tokens): adjust --gold2 lightness by +5%
```

## Pre-commit checklist (run before every commit)
```bash
npm run lint          # zero warnings, zero errors
npm run typecheck     # zero TS errors
npm run build         # must complete without errors
```

## Deploy to Cloudflare Pages
```bash
npm run pages:deploy
# = npm run build && wrangler pages deploy out
```

## Environment variables
Required in `.env.local` (never commit this file):
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://sanja-krstic.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxx.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...
```
On Cloudflare Pages: add these under **Settings → Environment variables**.

## .gitignore (already set, do not remove)
- `.env.local`, `.env`
- `.next/`, `out/`
- `node_modules/`
- `.DS_Store`

## Post-deploy verification
1. Open production URL in incognito
2. Check: hero video loads, 3D canvas renders, smooth scroll works
3. Run Lighthouse on production (not localhost) for accurate CWV
4. Check mobile: cursor hidden, touch interactions smooth, no horizontal scroll

